history.content:
Welcome UC Berkeley! IMC invites you to this exclusive information session where several IMC Engineers and Traders will share insight into life as an IMC Intern, as well as tips for standing out in our recruiting process.

When: Wednesday, March 2 @ 5pm PT

Where: Both Sibley Auditorium and Virtual

RSVP: https://jst.me/msh6

Specifically, they will share details on topics like: what led them to accept a full-time role at IMC vs. another company, their daily responsibilities as an intern, and some of their favorite projects and social events.

You will also get the opportunity to ask questions during the live Q&A panel at the end, as well as learn how to get into our 2023 recruiting process early.

We look forward to meeting you!
history.subject: IMC Infosession on 3/2
